vote.title: Authorize the following: (1) a conditional grant agreement with EmDev Fund, LLC or an affiliate thereof (“Developer”) for the development of the AT LAST! Project located at 405 East Overton Road, Dallas, Texas 75216 in an amount not to exceed $400,000.00; and (2) an increase in appropriations in an amount not to exceed $400,000.00 in the ECO (I) Fund - Not to exceed $400,000.00 - Financing: ECO (I) Fund (2017 General Obligation Bond Fund)
